metadata.name: Daenerys Targaryen
metadata.description:
This incredible coin with exquisite finishes in the first edition of the collection that we have to call CryptoThrones, you can find all the information available at cryptothrones.art

Daenerys Targaryen is a symbol of power through leadership and inspiration of the people. She transmits that virtue that men on earth yearn to achieve transcendence and the transformation of power without borders, something symbolically similar to the Blockchain revolution. Welcome!
